        ✨ Welcome To Kevat Raj Kartik Hotel ✨ Best Chai In Town ✨
      </marquee>
      <a class="btn" href="https://wa.me/917354973753">Order on WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </header>  <section>
    <h2>Our Products</h2><div class="products">
  <div class="card">
